# {{senseid|mul|Q47083}} [[ohm#English:_Q47083|ohm]], the [[unit]] of [[electrical resistance]] in the [[International System of Units]].
====Usage notes==== * {{w|The Unicode Standard}} states that {{codepoint|U+2126|link=0}} is included in Unicode only for backward compatibility reasons. {{codepoint|U+03A9|link=0}} is preferred to represent ohms.
